<p>I've read Steve's nice blog series "<a href="http://blog.shoesrb.com/post/1453664385/other-ruby-gui-toolkits-shoes">Other Ruby GUI toolkits</a>" before.<p />I love <a href="http://blog.shoesrb.com/post/1480014928/other-ruby-gui-toolkits-qtruby">Search Sample</a>. :)<br /><a href="https://github.com/ashbb/green_shoes"><br />Green Shoes</a> doesn't aim to fully compatibility with <a href="https://github.com/shoes/shoes">Red Shoes</a>.<p />And at that time, Green Shoes had not enough capabilities.<p /> But now, let me show you a tiny code for Green Shoes. ;-)<p />Online Demo : <a href="http://www.rin-shun.com/shoes/search_sample_with_red_shoes.swf.html">Red Shoes</a> / <a href="http://www.rin-shun.com/shoes/search_sample_with_green_shoes.swf.html">Green Shoes</a><p />Code : <a href="http://github.com/shoes/shoes-contrib/raw/master/basic/search.rb">Red Shoes</a> / <a href="https://gist.github.com/701880">Green Shoes</a><p />Hope you'll like it,<br />ashbb</p>]]></content:encoded>
